column5: I'll have to agree with Pete on this one, Fishouflage IS cool! Would make a nice alternative to the current jerseys, but I don't think most sponsors would like that.  http://youtu.be/DK-uSugsT6g
fishouflage is his sponsor...  whats the difference?  hes just pushing product... that was basically a commercial...
Please send any problems you might have with threads to Admin/Mods. This is how threads go awry. Thanks bucket loads.
sorry roy... didnt mean it like that...  i just saw it as a more creative way to push a great product...
I see your point Musky Mike. These Vents are made to be fun, you should know by now not to take Pete very seriously, especially if you think he is 'bad mouthing' anything.
